metadata.name: FLUF Haus Cityscape- LA 2022 Poster
metadata.description:
One of  400 Jim Evans FLUF Haus Cityscape LA Posters from FLUF Haus LA at the Peterson Auto museum in Feb 2022.
 FLUF Haus is an immersive experience like no other. A night of art, music and revelry, with an incredible line-up of artists, installations and night-long entertainment, and featuring angelbaby, T Pain and Chromeo. FLUF Haus LA Celebrates 6 months of FLUF World and is the first event welcoming Party Bears into the FLUF World metaverse mix. Together our mission is to give artists and creative communities spaces to thrive, collaborate and create together.
 We are proud and incredibly lucky to have the one and only Jim Evans as our poster artist at FLUF Haus, treasure this NFT, it is the key to many great moments in the future. Bunnies up FLUFFLE...
